{"tid":1680583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］唔好叫popo 做「呀sir」，明明本來係佢地服侍你","createTime":"2019-10-29T02:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T05:24:07.000Z","uid":35699,"like":287,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"476bf5549b3617d433de146304d3237ffb45f72a","tid":1680583,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"可以叫佢警員，睇唔到冧巴就叫先生小姐，佢唔值得有尊稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係示範，應該用指令式句子同佢講嘢，同埋避免講「唔好」，因為人類對「唔好」呢個字無咁敏感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢位先生好激動，請你保持冷靜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀sir冷靜啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蒙面著綠色衫，手持電筒嘅先生即刻放低你嘅電筒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀sir唔好照我"},{"pid":"f8ef59c61db27b95cbabec38918ba3ff6b4cb30a","tid":1680583,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f70f4add35b1e48c72292b9053b8bee81332a927","tid":1680583,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLdavJJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLdavJJ.gif&h=943b7306&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76614b31d308192b4046b7a98671df27ce424b0c","tid":1680583,"uid":38885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"ec1b9aaa06de0328af6cef3748176da63b707c42","tid":1680583,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:11:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53657b237f23ed2305f4ea4793ba93015697d275","tid":1680583,"uid":206080,"li